  "subject": "Add prolog filter for INFO.yaml handling",
  "commit_message": "Add prolog filter for INFO.yaml handling\n\nThis is RELENG-1995\n\nIn essence:\n1) deny right for people to upload more than info.yaml file if info.yaml is in there\n2) If only info.yaml, then has to require non interactive users has to give a +1\n    Require Jenkins to give +1 if info.yaml file is in the change.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\n\nSigned-off-by: Bengt Thuree <bthuree@linuxfoundation.org>\nChange-Id: I99d94477ddec6a4c282bf8a43729ceaaa41ec9b9\n",
